Margaret Webster https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_Webster 0 Margaret Webster (March 15, 1905 – November 13, 1972) was an American-British theater actress, producer and director. Critic George Jean Nathan described her as "the best director of the plays of Shakespeare that we have".
